data.description: **Assumable 4% VA interest rate!** Nestled in a serene, gated neighborhood, this exquisite 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home promises both comfort and elegance. Its captivating high ceilings accentuate the spaciousness of the open-concept living, dining, and kitchen areas, providing an inviting atmosphere perfect for both entertaining and relaxation. The heart of the home is undoubtedly the generously sized kitchen, complete with a sizeable island that doubles as a breakfast bar. Modern appliances and abundant storage complement the space. An added gem, the built-in hutch, not only provides additional storage but brings a touch of vintage charm to this contemporary home. Cozy up during cooler evenings by the elegant fireplace, which stands as a focal point in the living area, lending warmth and ambiance to the space. For those who need a dedicated workspace or simply a quiet retreat, the fourth bedroom is versatile enough to be transformed into a home office, ensuring work-from-home days are both productive and peaceful. On the opposite end of the home, find your sanctuary in the expansive Primary Suite with an additional seating area. This luxurious retreat boasts a vast bathroom, complete with double vanities ensuring ample space for personal care routines. Unwind after long days in the jacuzzi tub, or if you prefer a quicker refresh, a separate walk-around shower stands at the ready. Completing the suite is a large walk-in closet, ready-to-house wardrobes of all sizes and seasons. This residence perfectly marries functionality with sophistication, ensuring every member of the family feels right at home.  The home also has an above-ground storm shelter, a full sprinkler system, landscaping front and back, as well as walking trails and fishing pond in community. Great highway access and close proximity to Tinker, Boeing, Heart Hospital South, shopping, and Downtown OKC. This home is an OG&E Positive Energy Rated home.
